subproject.description: This project is to build and strengthen entrepreneurial capacity of Nauruans to confidently engage in a variety of individual enterprises that will provide a sustainable livelihood to those who are currently unemployed or underemployed.  particular emphasis will be given on empowering women and young people to engage in dignified work and self employment
subproject.title: NR Entrepreneurship Dev
